data.description: This home is a must-see! A two story haven with a 3-car garage that caters to all your needs, from parking to storage, in a desirable neighborhood. This home features 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and loft. Entertain guests in the open concept kitchen/dining/living area, just in time for football season and the holidays. This home provides 3 bedrooms upstairs (including the primary) with two full bathrooms as well as one generously sized bedroom downstairs with its own 3/4 bathroom making this home great for out of town guests. Other features include: granite countertops throughout, stainless steel appliances in kitchen, large utility room in house, and front and backyard landscaping.
